        "text": "3. On 10 May 1952 Lt. Col. LUCIUS L. FREE, Headquarters OSI, was\ninterviewed and furnished the writer with a copy of a TAI received from\nthe Air Intelligence Center, Wright-Patterson AFB. Information con-\ntained in the TAI is summarized as follows:"
      },
